-- Unification Church Says Leader Moon Is ‘Gravely Ill’
-- B y   S a n g w o n   Y o o n
-- 2012-08-16T00:28:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-16/unification-church-says-leader-moon-is-gravely-ill-.html
Unification Church founder Moon Sun
Myung is gravely ill and has been put on a respirator at the
intensive care unit of St. Mary’s Hospital in  Seoul , church
spokesman Ahn Ho Yeol said today by telephone.  Moon, 92, was admitted on Aug. 14 after suffering from a
cold and pneumonia earlier this month and developing
complications, Ahn said. Moon’s condition has not changed since
his hospitalization and doctors are still conducting tests, Ahn
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sangwon Yoon in Seoul at 
